Go get the fuck outta here.

10:09.342 --> 10:11.211
That's not right, Wren.

10:11.244 --> 10:12.846
Man, shut up.

10:18.118 --> 10:19.953
Hey, yo, Tris!

10:24.825 --> 10:28.762
I'm comin' back for my shit, man.
Believe it.

10:28.796 --> 10:30.556
You know you better
hurry the fuck up, right?

10:34.835 --> 10:36.670
I just wanted to thank you...

10:36.704 --> 10:39.039
for what you tried
to do for us back there.

10:39.072 --> 10:41.317
Well, it's okay. I'm glad you're all right.
I'll see you later.

10:41.341 --> 10:45.278
Wait, wait, wait, wait.
What's your name? Martine.

10:45.312 --> 10:48.782
Wow. You go to the Burke? Yeah.
We have algebra together.

10:48.816 --> 10:51.919
Right, right. I forgot.
Well, I'll see you in school then.

10:51.952 --> 10:54.021
Not if I see you first.

10:54.054 --> 10:56.356
Bye.
Bye.

10:56.389 --> 10:59.192
Man. "Bye."

10:59.226 --> 11:01.261
"Bye." I like that.

11:01.294 --> 11:03.731
Come on, my man.
Hey, dawg, that girl is fine.

11:03.764 --> 11:06.867
No joke. No joke. Shit.
Come on over here.

11:09.770 --> 11:13.907
Well, goddamn.

11:13.941 --> 11:16.777
Y'all little pimps
look fucked up.

11:16.810 --> 11:19.412
Twinkie!
Wassup, Twinkie?

11:19.446 --> 11:21.882
Hey, baby! Wassup, man?
What's that?

11:21.915 --> 11:24.151
You're just what we want, Twinkie.
Wassup, Twinkie?

11:24.184 --> 11:26.787
Wassup, man? What's happenin'?
What the fuck happened to y'all?

11:30.057 --> 11:32.726
Hey, man. Sometimes you gotta
fight to keep what's yours.

11:32.760 --> 11:36.029
- You know how that shit go. - Hell,
yeah. Ain't that the motherfuckin' truth?

11:36.063 --> 11:38.098
You got a little ho
to take care of you?

11:38.131 --> 11:41.101
No, man. We good.
We can take care of ourselves.

11:41.134 --> 11:43.336
Look here, man.

11:46.239 --> 11:49.176
Get you a ho.
All right?

11:49.209 --> 11:52.145
Buy her somethin' nice.
Treat her like somethin' special.

11:52.179 --> 11:55.348
Shit. You take care of your ho's,
your ho's will take care of you.

11:55.382 --> 11:58.919
Hell of a lot better than this
beat-up-lookin' motherfucker right here.

12:03.023 --> 12:05.225
- Hey, thanks, Twinkie.
- All right. Y'all take care.

12:05.258 --> 12:07.294
Hey, Twinkie?

12:07.327 --> 12:10.397
Man, where all your ho's?

12:10.430 --> 12:12.866
Let me learn you
somethin', young pimp.

12:12.900 --> 12:17.170
Them ho's is for dough,
not for show. All right?

12:17.204 --> 12:21.942
All right, Twinkie.

12:21.975 --> 12:24.377
Twinkie was always
tellin' us off.

12:24.411 --> 12:28.982
And you know, it never dawned on
us to ask why. I'm getting me a ho.

12:29.016 --> 12:31.084
Are you sure we should
be doin' this?

12:31.118 --> 12:33.553
My grandmother's
at choir practice at the church.

12:33.586 --> 12:36.456
Man, you sure?
Yes, I'm sure.

12:39.927 --> 12:43.997
Hoo. Light that bud.
Yeah, man.

12:44.031 --> 12:46.299
Yeah, that's it.
Hoo-wee!

12:46.333 --> 12:48.035
That's it.

12:50.403 --> 12:53.106
Hell, yeah, man.
That's smokin'.

12:53.140 --> 12:55.242
Man, give it to me.

12:57.410 --> 13:01.348
Yeah.
Yeah, okay.

13:06.486 --> 13:09.923
Yeah. Yeah, yeah.
Now that's smokin'.

13:09.957 --> 13:12.425
Where you learn that from?
Come on now, baby.

13:12.459 --> 13:15.228
Y'all don't know
everything about me now.

13:15.262 --> 13:19.299
Did y'all hear what Wren said today?
He said we had heart.

13:19.332 --> 13:22.302
That was bomb-ass shit to say.
E-Bone's Uncle Pee Wee...

13:22.335 --> 13:26.006
is the kind of guy that could never quite get
it together. What you think you're doin'?

13:26.039 --> 13:29.977
You know the type... wears jacked-up
clothes, can't keep a job...

13:30.010 --> 13:33.622
The kind of guy you have to be in the mood to
hang around with. Thirty-four-year-old fuckup.

13:33.646 --> 13:35.615
You ain't gonna say nothin'
to Nana, right?

13:35.648 --> 13:38.218
Shit. You better
believe I am.

13:38.251 --> 13:41.421
Let up on that smoke! Man, all right.
Damn. Just take a hit.

13:41.454 --> 13:43.423
Don't he?
He's a has-been.

13:43.456 --> 13:46.259
Always comin' round.
Broke has-been.

13:46.293 --> 13:49.462
