Want you do a favor for me.

13:49.496 --> 13:52.065
You mean smokin' my shit up
ain't enough?

13:52.099 --> 13:55.335
Why don't you and your
partners go take a run for me?

13:55.368 --> 13:57.905
Then we straight after that?

13:57.938 --> 14:01.141
Like a hard-on in the mornin'.

14:01.174 --> 14:03.576
