- I'll handle it.

14:08.081 --> 14:09.849
Cool. I don't even like Pee Wee.

14:13.921 --> 14:17.224
Brick! Shit. Y'all can't do it.

14:17.257 --> 14:19.927
Who can't?
You shouldn't have said that shit.

14:30.637 --> 14:33.140
Simon!

14:34.541 --> 14:37.945
Shit.

14:41.681 --> 14:44.417
Y'all a'ight?
Yeah, I think so.

14:44.451 --> 14:48.155
Yeah, man. That's cool.
All right, come on. Let's go.

14:48.188 --> 14:50.190
The fuck.

14:53.426 --> 14:56.696
Yo, Simon. Come on, man.
Let's go.

15:02.302 --> 15:05.272
Shit.
That's Mr. Thomas.

15:05.305 --> 15:07.507
The social studies teacher?

15:07.540 --> 15:10.177
Damn. That is him.

15:10.210 --> 15:12.946
Man, even scholarly-type
motherfuckers gotta get they smoke on.

15:12.980 --> 15:17.384
Hey, that's why that motherfucker's
always happy in class and shit.

15:17.417 --> 15:20.120
'Cause he was gettin' faded
in the teachers' lounge.

15:20.153 --> 15:22.990
If you wanted weed, you
could go just about anywhere.

15:23.023 --> 15:25.058
I mean, there were plenty
of dealers out there...

15:25.092 --> 15:27.127
who would sell you
a nickel or a dime bag...

15:27.160 --> 15:30.563
of just about whatever it was
you were into.

15:30.597 --> 15:35.035
But for variety
and that really good stuff...

15:35.068 --> 15:38.571
and for the dealer who never
ran out of your favorite stash,

15:38.605 --> 15:41.041
you had to go to Sam's place.

15:41.074 --> 15:43.076
Yo, who's winning?

15:43.110 --> 15:45.245
Sox. Last inning.
Rice just doubled.

15:45.278 --> 15:49.582
Damn. Pee Wee must be feelin' pretty
good let you come out after dark.

15:49.616 --> 15:54.087
Usual? Nah. He want four Thai
sticks and two ounces of the Buddha.

15:54.121 --> 15:56.121
All right. You wait right here.
I'll be right back.

15:57.624 --> 16:00.693
And look, don't none of you little
motherfuckers touch my food,

16:00.727 --> 16:03.596
especially you,
you little fat fucker.

16:03.630 --> 16:06.066
Hey, fuck you.
Who the fuck is he callin' fat?

16:06.099 --> 16:08.101
- Your fat ass.
- Fuck you.

16:15.142 --> 16:17.210
What the fuck you...

16:17.244 --> 16:21.181
