What's wrong with you?

16:39.199 --> 16:41.434
Come on, E-Bone!
We gotta get goin'!

16:41.468 --> 16:43.670
Come on, man! We gotta go!
We gotta go!

16:43.703 --> 16:45.438
Go, go, go!
Go, go!

16:54.281 --> 16:56.316
Hey, man, anybody comin'?

16:56.349 --> 16:59.319
